Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

IMAPAccount main
Host imap.gmail.com
User m.redaelli@gmail.com
PassCmd "secret-tool lookup user m.redaelli domain gmail.com"
SSLType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN

IMAPStore main-remote
Account main

MaildirStore main-local
Path ~/Maildir/main/
Inbox ~/Maildir/main/inbox
Subfolders Verbatim

Channel main-inbox
Master :main-remote:
Slave :main-local:
Pattern * ![Gmail]* !drafts !spam !sent !trash

Channel main-spam
Master :main-remote:"[Gmail]/Spam"
Slave :main-local:spam

Channel main-draft
Master :main-remote:"[Gmail]/Drafts"
Slave :main-local:drafts

Channel main-sent
Master :main-remote:"[Gmail]/Sent Mail"
Slave :main-local:sent

Channel main-trash
Master :main-remote:"[Gmail]/Trash"
Slave :main-local:trash

Group main
Channel main-inbox
Channel main-draft
Channel main-spam
Channel main-sent
Channel main-trash



